{"tid":1938273,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"非必要情況下仲踏出家門嘅你，我非常鼓勵你繼續出","createTime":"2020-03-22T12:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T13:20:13.000Z","uid":38563,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4f73375828aef1d3b1a9e21560cc6ef4888a98","tid":1938273,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"而家條街帶毒人數其實仲係好少，俾盡咪幾百個，去一去行山又或者出mk食個飯嘅感染機率分分鐘仲低過俾車撞，更何況已經全民戴晒口罩<br />\n<br />\n所以我係極之鼓勵你哋繼續出街<br />\n<br />\n多啲人出街先至多啲機會係一個咁低機率感染嘅情況下都仲有咁多人可以感染到<br />\n多啲人感染到先至可以增加帶毒者嘅基數<br />\n增加基數先至可以令每次出街感染病毒嘅機率上升至高過俾車撞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最終先至冇人敢出街，然後抗疫成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n繼續非必要都繼續出街，你哋嘅犧牲係抗疫成功不可或缺嘅齒輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e178a734134318a6c98f4b673617a83bfa197c","tid":1938273,"uid":38563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"屋企好悶，出一出門冇事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db747b0d5b5d0b23491c296a4345ecb526a95dde","tid":1938273,"uid":38563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"屋企食飯食到好悶，出旺角食餐好先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4897f025dd04634e9aa9f95de9a01ed4028af76a","tid":1938273,"uid":38563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"同fd好耐冇見，得閒約佢食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170554e537c670e35ced6925fad992824a220a2f","tid":1938273,"uid":38563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:23:16.000Z","msg":"落街跑步冇事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做運動咁健康"},{"pid":"cb2e4b86c0d65630bade879fa56e1a8521c047e2","tid":1938273,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:28:15.